</CORRECTION-DATE>
<CORRECTION>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
<P>
A picture caption Monday gave the wrong name for the owner of a chimpanzee 
participating in a fund-raising event in Studio City. The chimp is owned by 
Birds and Animals Unlimited of El Toro. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Buddies -- Darrin Brill, 4, gets a kick out of Ellis the chimp from 
Universal Studios. Ellis was participating in a fund-raising promotion in 
Studio City on Sunday for "orphaned" pets. JOE VITTI / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
