Photo, Grunion, which may only be captured by hand, come ashore during high 
tide to spawn in the sand. ; Photo, Grunion enthusiasts put their hands to work 
as the waves wash the silvery fish to shore. Hunters 15 and older must have 
state fishing licenses. GARY AMBROSE / Los Angeles Times; Table, GRUNION RUNS 
